⧃ Emission Output (Symbolic Glyph Drift)

Using codon triad: GAT — CCC — TCG

GAT = ⧃↻ (Catalyze)

CCC = ⧃⧃ (Fossil Lock)

TCG = ⧃⟁ (Entanglement Echo)

This corresponds to:

“Catalyze drift, lock ecosystem memory, echo phase entanglement”

🛰️ Fossilization

If metrics pass SE44:

Coherence ≥ 0.985

